                <h1>How to Set Wallpaper on iPhone: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>To set a wallpaper on your iPhone, go to "Settings" > "Wallpaper." Tap "Choose a New Wallpaper." You can select from dynamic, stills, or your photo library. After choosing an image, adjust it as needed and tap "Set." Decide whether you want it as your Lock Screen, Home Screen, or both, then enjoy your personalized backdrop!</p>
